<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِعَلِيٍّ:</span> <span class="c2">(أَنْتَ مِنِّي وَأَنَا مِنْكَ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
